article_id:2525,category_name:News,title_name:Regarding an Issue with Gala Zethia's Bahamut,image_path:,message:<div>We have confirmed the following issue with the adventurer Gala Zethia.</div><div><br></div><div>After being summoned by Gala Zethia, Bahamut may stop moving if a helper skill is used during certain stages in the combo or under the effects of certain skills.</div><div><br></div><div>We are planning to address this issue at a later date. Any further information will be posted to this notice.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1632981600,update_time1632899334